product.name: Fake Bake Blush Legal Sunburn
product.description:
Give your cheeks a sun kissed glow with Fake Bake Blush in Legal Sunburn. Paraben Free. Brush the powder blush over your cheeks, nose, and brow arches, and instantly wake up a tired or pale face.
The naturally derived red and pink hues give you a fresh, sexy color-minus the skin damage.Ingredients: Mica, Talc, Nylon-12, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Parafinum Liquidum, Petrolatum, Kaolin, Magnesium Stearate, Tocopheryl Acetate, Caprylic/Capric, Triglyceride, Silica, Phenoxyethanol, Proctone Olamine, [may contain ( +/-): C!75470, CI77891, CI77499, CI45410:2, CI77492, CI19140:1]
